{"tid":174942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山寨校巴】幼稚園學生拋出車被輾死","createTime":"2017-03-27T07:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T08:44:41.000Z","uid":55400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc7799000d9de058a4798591ad1f275eeb4b782","tid":174942,"uid":55400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"河南濮陽台前縣日前發生奪命車禍，一名4歲幼稚園學生乘坐校巴時，從車廂掉下，繼而被輾死。目前，肇事司機已被控制，園方已和家屬就後續賠償事宜達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n台前縣清水河鄉的王先生表示，上周三下午5時許，4歲孫兒瑞瑞放學乘校巴回家，校車離家僅有幾十米時，瑞瑞突然從車上跌落，再被車輪輾過死亡。瑞瑞的母親在家門等候時，看到校車輾過了一個東西，沒想到是自己的孩子。<br />\n<br />\n出事之後，全鎮的幼兒園都停課了。涉事校巴被警方扣查。該校巴為一部深藍色客貨車，除了前排座椅外，其餘座位已被拆除，車廂內放置23張圓凳。據王先生透露，幼稚園平時都是用該車接送學生。當地教育部門表示，沒有審批一輛正規校車予幼稚園。<br />\n<br />\n據警方透露，涉事司機已被刑拘，幼稚園已和瑞瑞的家人達成賠償協議，園方支付35萬元人民幣作為賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170327&amp;guid=56484886&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170327%26guid%3D56484886%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b39eb595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170327%26guid%3D56484886%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=0793ad86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170327&amp;guid=56484886&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"8eee021525f9438c51524e2fc4d49a4d9e7059bb","tid":174942,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"又一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044ca659d15ffd8770d235f3dcea8322360d5b59","tid":174942,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}